context-free syntax

  Number.Integer            = UNSIGNED-INT
  Number.Decimal            = UNSIGNED-DECIMAL
  String.String             = LEGACY10-STRING
  Boolean.True              = <true> {case-insensitive}
  Boolean.False             = <false> {case-insensitive}
  BindVariable.BindVariable = <?>
